{"tw": {"2920030": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "UnderGirl: Submission Path", "steam_appid": 2920030, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "controller_support": "full", "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920030/extras/704e41777b3c2f0e153e1fdfeee78fc1.avif?t=1770978009\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920030/extras_big/704e41777b3c2f0e153e1fdfeee78fc1.avif?t=1770978009 width=800 height=94 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你只是一個熱愛格鬥與武術的普通人。 你努力訓練，在一場又一場比賽中脫穎而出，贏得了不錯的聲譽。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在大學生活的枯燥和平庸對手的刺激下，你決定參加一場地下格鬥錦標賽。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而，令你震驚的是，你的對手竟然是......一位女性！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920030/extras/32a772a85fca8e525b93f4eb0c36aa67.poster.avif?t=1770978009\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920030/extras/32a772a85fca8e525b93f4eb0c36aa67.webm?t=1770978009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920030/extras/32a772a85fca8e525b93f4eb0c36aa67.mp4?t=1770978009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >若輸給她，你的人生可能將徹底改變。 不只是打擊自信，更可能引發身邊女孩對你態度的轉變。 <br>曾經尊重你的她們，或許會開始把你當作一個喜歡被支配、被欺負的怪人。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920030/extras/704e41777b3c2f0e153e1fdfeee78fc1.avif?t=1770978009\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920030/extras_big/704e41777b3c2f0e153e1fdfeee78fc1.avif?t=1770978009 width=800 height=94 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是否曾經想過：「天哪，我真希望她用大腿夾爆我的腦袋！ 」？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果是的話......</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >UnderGirl: SP 是一款以女性支配為主題的遊戲，你必須擊敗這些美麗的女孩，才能重新奪回屬於你的尊嚴！ <br>遊戲擁有一個簡單卻有策略性的格鬥系統：5個方向的格擋選擇，你需要觀察對手的動作，猜測她們即將發起哪種攻擊，並予以反制。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但要小心——她們會毫不猶豫地使用各種卑鄙招式來讓你束手就擒。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920030/extras/f43d58f34d00d0c8288c04ba3ee633ba.avif?t=1770978009\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920030/extras_big/f43d58f34d00d0c8288c04ba3ee633ba.avif?t=1770978009 width=1600 height=900 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >請記住：如果你做出了糟糕的選擇，戰鬥的結果可能遠不止輸一場那麼簡單。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在地下格鬥圈中，可沒有什麼規則或底線。 在你還沒反應過來之前，一切就可能已經結束了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920030/extras/6cad22cff00539cf4972936d0708bb0d.avif?t=1770978009\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920030/extras_big/6cad22cff00539cf4972936d0708bb0d.avif?t=1770978009 width=800 height=94 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920030/extras/2a296c3b96854b66876f18de2d63b0be.avif?t=1770978009\" width=616 height=413 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920030/extras/dae57d5dc1533ea2aa957128b4ed813a.avif?t=1770978009\" width=616 height=399 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920030/extras/48c265644e6e83499b33f0ce226dc187